                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">For KoBold</h4>
                <p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300">I'll build strategic programs that leverage data insights while keeping human judgment at the center</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-3">My Strategic Experience</h4>
