                  <li>• Implemented ADKAR change management for complex transformations</li>
                  <li>• Designed compensation frameworks that balance market data with culture</li>
                  <li>• Built talent councils and succession planning for technical roles</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
